channel.title: Seven of Seven
channel.description: Join Chief and Johnny as they explore the legendary cinematic masterpiece that set the world ablaze: SEVEN (No, not that one). They dissect the film in seven minute segments, unpacking the wild, wet, and weird world of Andy Sidaris and attempt to stay (relatively) sane in the process. SPOILER: They fail.
